"supports up to 12 USB ports, and has support for <xref linkend=\"gloss-vt-"
"acronym-sata\"/> and <xref linkend=\"gloss-vt-acronym-iommu\"/> . <!-- IRQ "
"routing has also been improved. -->"
msgstr ""
