#: libvirt_configuration_virsh.xml:934
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following procedure uses example data. Make sure to replace it by "
"appropriate data from your setup."
msgstr ""
"下記に示す手順は構成例となります。お使いの環境に合わせて各種のデータを変更し"
